  m_text: "Drag the sliders \u2014 the glow reacts in real time. Each control publishes
    its value to a signal stream; a NeoSignalParamBinding on the shape remaps it
    onto an effect param. No UnityEvents, no glue code \u2014 the link round-trips
    through the spec."
